#

Pork Picnic Platter

135 min
$40
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodFamily Meal

Description

A delightful assortment of slow-cooked pork paired with fresh sides and tangy sauces, perfect for a laid-back gathering!

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 3 lbs
  • bbq sauce: 1 cup
  • coleslaw mix: 4 cups
  • green onions: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • pickles: 1 cup, sliced
  • hawaiian rolls: 12 rolls
  • corn on the cob: 4 ears
  • butter: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1 tsp
